<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>12 недель в году | Годовая система</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: { extend: { colors: { 'brand-purple': '#5c4bdf' } } }
        }
    </script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Sans:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="images/logo.svg">
    <link rel="alternate icon" type="image/png" href="images/logo-icon.png">

    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="12 Недель">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="images/logo-icon.png">
    
    <link rel="manifest" href="manifest.json">

    <style>
        body { font-family: 'IBM Plex Sans', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; overflow-x: hidden; }
        .bg-sidebar { background-color: #f4f6fa; }
        .page-view { display: none; }
        .page-view.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.2s ease-out; }
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(5px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 4px; height: 4px; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background-color: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 4px; }
        .custom-scrollbar::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background-color: transparent; }
        .bonus-card { transition: all 0.3s ease; }
        .bonus-card.achieved { background-color: #fff; border-color: #fbbf24; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.15); }
        .bonus-locked { opacity: 0.6; }
        textarea, input[type="text"], input[type="number"], select { color: #1e293b; }
        textarea { overflow: hidden; resize: none; }
        .goal-edit-input { transition: all 0.2s; border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; }
        .goal-edit-input:hover { border-bottom: 2px solid #cbd5e1; }
        .goal-edit-input:focus { border-bottom: 2px solid #5c4bdf; background-color: #fff; outline: none; }
        .vision-input { transition: background 0.2s; }
        .vision-input:hover { background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.02); cursor: text; }
        .vision-input:focus { background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); outline: none; box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px rgba(92, 75, 223, 0.2); border-radius: 6px; }
        
        .vision-image-card { background-size: cover; background-position: center; background-color: #f1f5f9; transition: all 0.3s ease; cursor: pointer; position: relative; border-radius: 1rem; border: 2px dashed #cbd5e1; }
        .vision-image-card:hover { border-color: #5c4bdf; background-color: #eef2ff; }
        .vision-image-card.has-image { border-style: solid; border-color: transparent; }
        .vision-image-card::after { content: ''; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 60%); border-radius: inherit; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
        .vision-image-card.has-image::after { opacity: 1; }
        
        .vision-upload-icon { position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); transition: all 0.2s; z-index: 20; color: #94a3b8; }
        .vision-image-card:hover .vision-upload-icon { color: #5c4bdf; transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1); }
        .vision-image-card.has-image .vision-upload-icon { display: none !important; }
        .vision-image-card.has-image .empty-text { display: none; }
        
        .delete-img-btn { opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; transition: opacity 0.2s ease; z-index: 30; }
        .vision-image-card.has-image:hover .delete-img-btn { opacity: 0.8; pointer-events: auto; }
        .delete-img-btn:hover { opacity: 1 !important; }
        .vision-image-card.has-image:hover { filter: brightness(0.95); }
    </style>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@supabase/supabase-js@2"></script>
</head>
<body class="flex h-screen overflow-hidden text-slate-800 w-full max-w-full">
    
    <div id="authOverlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-slate-100 z-50 flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full max-w-md border border-slate-200">
            <h2 id="authTitle" class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-purple mb-2 text-center">Вход</h2>
            <p id="authSubtitle" class="text-slate-500 text-xs sm:text-sm text-center mb-6 sm:mb-8">Войдите, чтобы синхронизировать прогресс</p>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
                <div id="nameFieldGroup" class="hidden">
                    <label class="block text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1">Ваше Имя</label>
                    <input type="text" id="authName" class="w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="Например: Иван Иванов">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="authEmail" class="w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="your@email.com">
                </div>
                <div>
                    <label class="block text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1">Пароль</label>
                    <input type="password" id="authPassword" class="w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-3 border border-slate-200 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 outline-none transition-all" placeholder="Минимум 6 символов">
                </div>
                
                <p id="authErrorMsg" class="text-rose-500 text-xs font-bold text-center hidden"></p>
                
                <div class="pt-2 sm:pt-4 flex flex-col gap-2 sm:gap-3">
                    <button id="btnSubmitAuth" class="w-full bg-brand-purple text-white rounded-xl py-3 sm:py-3.5 text-sm font-bold hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-md">Войти</button>
                    <button id="btnToggleAuth" class="w-full text-slate-500 text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold hover:text-brand-purple transition-colors mt-1 sm:mt-2 p-2">Нет аккаунта? Регистрация</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="sidebarOverlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-slate-900/50 z-30 hidden lg:hidden transition-opacity opacity-0"></div>

    <aside id="sidebar" class="absolute z-40 inset-y-0 left-0 w-64 bg-sidebar flex flex-col justify-between h-full border-r border-slate-200 shrink-0 transform -translate-x-full lg:relative lg:translate-x-0 transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out">
        <div>
            <div class="p-6">
                <img src="images/logo.svg" alt="12 Недель Логотип" class="w-16 h-16 mb-2" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                <h1 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-purple leading-tight tracking-tight">12 недель<br>в году</h1>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-2 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Годовая система</p>
            </div>
            <nav class="px-4 space-y-2">
                <button data-target="dashboard" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 bg-white text-brand-purple rounded-xl shadow-sm text-sm font-semibold transition-colors">
                    <span class="mr-3 text-lg">🚀</span> Дашборд
                </button>
                <button data-target="plan" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                    <span class="mr-3 text-lg">🎯</span> Планы и цели
                </button>
                <button data-target="rewards" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                    <span class="mr-3 text-lg">🎁</span> Бонусы
                </button>
                <button data-target="reflection" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                    <span class="mr-3 text-lg">📓</span> Рефлексия
                </button>
                <button data-target="vision" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                    <span class="mr-3 text-lg">🔭</span> Личное видение
                </button>
            </nav>
        </div>
        <div class="px-4 pb-6 mt-auto border-t border-slate-200/60 pt-4">
            <button data-target="profile" class="nav-btn w-full flex items-center px-4 py-3 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
                <span class="mr-3 text-lg">👤</span> Профиль
            </button>
        </div>
    </aside>

    <main class="flex-1 flex flex-col h-full overflow-hidden relative w-full max-w-full">
        <header class="py-3 flex flex-col xl:flex-row items-start xl:items-center justify-between px-4 lg:px-8 border-b border-slate-200 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md shrink-0 sticky top-0 z-20 gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full max-w-full">
            
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between w-full xl:w-auto min-w-0">
                <div class="flex items-center min-w-0 flex-1 pr-2 gap-2 sm:gap-3">
                    <img src="images/logo.svg" alt="Логотип" class="w-8 h-8 sm:w-10 sm:h-10 shrink-0" onerror="this.style.display='none'">
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center min-w-0 flex-1 pr-2">
                        <span id="headerTitle" class="text-brand-purple font-bold text-sm sm:text-lg leading-tight sm:leading-none mb-0.5 sm:mb-1 truncate">Твой прогресс</span>
                        <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[11px] text-slate-500 font-medium uppercase tracking-wider flex items-center truncate">
                            <span class="mr-1">📅</span> Сегодня: <span id="todayDateDisplay" class="font-bold text-slate-700 ml-1 truncate">--</span>
                        </span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button id="mobileMenuBtn" class="lg:hidden p-2 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-brand-purple hover:text-white focus:outline-none transition-colors shrink-0">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 sm:w-6 sm:h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16"></path></svg>
                </button>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col bg-slate-50 p-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 w-full flex-1 xl:mx-6 overflow-x-auto custom-scrollbar" id="headerWeekSelectorBlock">
                <div class="w-full flex justify-between items-center mb-1.5 px-1 min-w-[240px]">
                    <span class="font-bold text-brand-purple text-[9px] sm:text-xs uppercase" id="currentBlockLabel">БЛОК 1</span>
                    <span class="text-[7px] sm:text-[9px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider bg-slate-200/70 px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-right ml-2 truncate">12 нед. фокуса + 1 отд.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full min-w-[240px]">
                    <div id="weekSelector" class="grid gap-[2px] w-full" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(13, minmax(0, 1fr));"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between xl:justify-end gap-2 sm:gap-4 w-full xl:w-auto shrink-0 min-w-0">
                <div id="userProfileBadge" class="hidden items-center gap-2 sm:gap-3 flex-1 min-w-0">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-start xl:items-end min-w-0">
                        <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">Вы вошли как</span>
                        <span id="userEmailDisplay" class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-700 truncate w-full max-w-[120px] sm:max-w-[150px]">--</span>
                    </div>
                    <button id="btnLogoutHeader" class="p-1.5 sm:p-2.5 text-slate-400 hover:text-rose-500 hover:bg-rose-50 rounded-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-rose-100 shrink-0" title="Выйти">
                        <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 16l4-4m0 0l-4-4m4 4H7m6 4v1a3 3 0 01-3 3H6a3 3 0 01-3-3V7a3 3 0 013-3h4a3 3 0 013 3v1"></path></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="w-px h-8 bg-slate-200 hidden xl:block shrink-0"></div>
                <button id="globalSaveBtn" class="bg-brand-purple hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white px-3 sm:px-5 py-2 sm:py-3 rounded-xl text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold shadow-md transition-all flex items-center shrink-0 justify-center flex-1 xl:flex-none min-w-0">
                    <span class="mr-1 sm:mr-2 text-sm sm:text-lg">💾</span> <span id="globalSaveBtnText" class="truncate">Сохранить</span>
                </button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="flex-1 overflow-y-auto overflow-x-hidden p-3 sm:p-4 lg:p-8 relative custom-scrollbar w-full" id="mainScrollArea">
            
            <div id="page-dashboard" class="page-view active w-full relative">
                
                <div class="sticky top-0 z-30 bg-[#f8fafc] pt-2 pb-3 sm:pb-4 -mx-3 sm:-mx-4 px-3 sm:px-4 lg:-mx-8 lg:px-8 mb-4 sm:mb-6 border-b border-slate-200/60 shadow-[0_10px_20px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] w-[calc(100%+1.5rem)] sm:w-[calc(100%+2rem)] lg:w-[calc(100%+4rem)]">
                    <div class="bg-brand-purple rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-5 shadow-md text-white flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between relative overflow-hidden gap-3 sm:gap-0">
                        <div class="absolute right-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-1/2 bg-[url('data:image/svg+xml;base64,PHN2ZyB3aWR0aD0iMjAiIGhlaWdodD0iMjAiIHhtbG5zPSJodHRwOi8vd3d3LnczLm9yZy8yMDAwL3N2ZyI+PGNpcmNsZSBjeD0iMiIgY3k9IjIiIHI9IjIiIGZpbGw9IiNmZmYiIGZpbGwtb3BhY2l0eT0iMC4xIi8+PC9zdmc+')] opacity-50"></div>
                        <div class="relative z-10 w-full sm:flex-1 text-center sm:text-left">
                            <p class="text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] md:text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Исполнение недели</p>
                            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-center sm:justify-start space-x-2 sm:space-x-3">
                                <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold" id="cycleSpeed">0%</h2>
                                <span class="text-white/80 text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] bg-white/10 px-2 py-1 rounded-full font-medium whitespace-nowrap">Цель: > 85%</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative z-10 w-full sm:w-1/2 sm:pl-4 md:pl-8">
                            <div class="h-1.5 sm:h-2 w-full bg-white/20 rounded-full overflow-hidden shadow-inner">
                                <div id="cycleProgressBar" class="h-full bg-white transition-all duration-700 ease-out" style="width: 0%"></div>
                            </div>
                            <p class="text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-white/70 mt-1.5 sm:mt-2 text-center sm:text-right font-medium" id="scoreDetails">0 / 0 очков</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-purple-50/50 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-indigo-100/50 mb-5 sm:mb-8 text-center">
                    <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-rose-600 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 block">Ваша Миссия</span>
                    <p class="text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl font-medium text-slate-800 italic mb-4 sm:mb-6 break-words" id="dashMissionText">Сформулируйте свою миссию во вкладке «Личное видение».</p>
                    <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-brand-purple uppercase tracking-widest mb-1.5 sm:mb-2 block border-t border-indigo-100 pt-3 sm:pt-5">Фокус на 12 недель</span>
                    <p class="text-[11px] sm:text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-medium italic break-words" id="dashVisionText">Сформулируйте видение на 12 недель во вкладке «Личное видение».</p>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-[0_2px_15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)] border border-slate-100 mb-5 sm:mb-8 overflow-hidden w-full">
                    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-start sm:items-end mb-3 sm:mb-6 w-full">
                        <div class="min-w-0 flex-1 w-full">
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center mb-1.5 sm:mb-2 gap-1.5 sm:gap-2">
                                <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-brand-purple uppercase tracking-wider truncate" id="dashBlockTitle">Фокус Блока 1</span>
                                <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] bg-brand-purple/10 text-brand-purple font-bold px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-0.5 sm:py-1 rounded whitespace-nowrap" id="dashBlockDates">--</span>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800" id="dashWeekTitle">Неделя 1</h2>
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-0.5 sm:mt-1" id="dashWeekDates">--</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-2 sm:mt-0 text-left sm:text-right w-full sm:w-auto border-t sm:border-t-0 border-slate-100 pt-2 sm:pt-0 shrink-0">
                            <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-700 capitalize tracking-wide" id="calendarMonthName">--</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full overflow-x-auto pb-1 sm:pb-2 -mx-1 px-1 sm:mx-0 sm:px-0 custom-scrollbar">
                        <div class="flex w-full gap-[2px] sm:gap-1 min-w-[260px] sm:min-w-[320px]" id="monthCalendarStrip"></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="dashboardGoalsContainer" class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 mb-8 w-full"></div>
                <div id="dashboardBlocksContainer" class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 mt-6 sm:mt-12 mb-6 sm:mb-8 w-full"></div>
            </div>

            <div id="page-plan" class="page-view w-full">
                <div class="bg-indigo-50/50 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl border border-indigo-100 mb-5 sm:mb-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center gap-3 sm:gap-6 shadow-sm w-full">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-auto">
                        <h2 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-bold text-slate-800 mb-0.5 sm:mb-1">Годовой Календарь</h2>
                        <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-500">Выберите понедельник для старта</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-1.5 sm:p-2 rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm w-full md:w-auto">
                        <input type="date" id="startDateInput" class="bg-transparent border-none text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none font-bold text-brand-purple cursor-pointer w-full">
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm font-medium text-slate-600 bg-white px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 sm:py-3 rounded-xl border border-indigo-200 shadow-sm flex-1 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-1 sm:gap-4 justify-between w-full">
                        <span>Начало: <span id="displayStartDate" class="font-bold text-slate-800">--</span></span>
                        <span>Финиш: <span id="displayEndDate" class="font-bold text-emerald-600">--</span></span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-5 sm:gap-8 w-full">
                    <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-5 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 w-full min-w-0">
                        <div class="flex gap-1 bg-slate-100 p-1 sm:p-1.5 rounded-xl w-full border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-x-auto custom-scrollbar pb-1.5">
                            <button class="plan-block-btn flex-1 py-1.5 sm:py-2 px-2 sm:px-1 rounded-lg text-[9px] xl:text-xs font-bold bg-white text-brand-purple shadow-sm transition-all whitespace-nowrap min-w-[80px] sm:min-w-0" data-block="1">Блок 1 (1-13)</button>
                            <button class="plan-block-btn flex-1 py-1.5 sm:py-2 px-2 sm:px-1 rounded-lg text-[9px] xl:text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 transition-all bg-transparent whitespace-nowrap min-w-[80px] sm:min-w-0" data-block="2">Блок 2 (14-26)</button>
                            <button class="plan-block-btn flex-1 py-1.5 sm:py-2 px-2 sm:px-1 rounded-lg text-[9px] xl:text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 transition-all bg-transparent whitespace-nowrap min-w-[80px] sm:min-w-0" data-block="3">Блок 3 (27-39)</button>
                            <button class="plan-block-btn flex-1 py-1.5 sm:py-2 px-2 sm:px-1 rounded-lg text-[9px] xl:text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-800 transition-all bg-transparent whitespace-nowrap min-w-[80px] sm:min-w-0" data-block="4">Блок 4 (40-52)</button>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 w-full min-w-0">
                            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Цели блока</h2>
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4 sm:mb-6">Вы можете <b class="text-brand-purple">редактировать</b> текст прямо в карточке.</p>
                            
                            <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 sm:p-5 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 mb-4 sm:mb-6 w-full">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-2 sm:mb-3">
                                    <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-brand-purple uppercase">Добавить цель</label>
                                    <span class="text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 bg-white px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-0.5 sm:py-1 rounded border border-slate-200" id="planCurrentBlockLabel">Блок 1</span>
                                </div>
                                <textarea id="newGoalTitle" placeholder="Например: Запустить продажи нового продукта" class="auto-resize w-full bg-white rounded-lg p-2.5 sm:p-4 border border-slate-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none mb-2 sm:mb-3 min-h-[3rem] sm:min-h-[4rem] focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 transition-all break-words"></textarea>
                                <button id="addGoalBtn" class="w-full bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">+ Создать цель</button>
                            </div>
                            <div id="goalsList" class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 max-h-[300px] sm:max-h-[500px] overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar pr-1 sm:pr-2 w-full"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-7 space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 w-full min-w-0">
                        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 w-full min-w-0">
                            <h2 class="text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-1 sm:mb-2">Практики и Тактики</h2>
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-slate-500 mb-4 sm:mb-6">Привяжите действия к целям <span class="font-bold text-brand-purple" id="taskSubBlockLabel">Блока 1</span>.</p>

                            <div class="bg-indigo-50/50 p-3 sm:p-6 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl border border-indigo-100 mb-5 sm:mb-8 w-full">
                                <div class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 w-full">
                                    <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">1. Выберите цель</label>
                                    <select id="taskGoalSelect" class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-2.5 sm:p-3 border border-indigo-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none font-medium text-brand-purple cursor-pointer shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 truncate"></select>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3 sm:mb-4 w-full">
                                    <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">2. Название практики</label>
                                    <input type="text" id="newTaskTitle" placeholder="Что нужно сделать?" class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-2.5 sm:p-3 border border-indigo-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50">
                                </div>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2.5 sm:gap-4 mb-4 sm:mb-6 w-full">
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">Тип</label>
                                        <select id="newTaskType" class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-2.5 sm:p-3 border border-indigo-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none cursor-pointer shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50">
                                            <option value="daily">☀️ Ежедневная</option>
                                            <option value="weekly">🎯 Еженедельная</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">Неделя</label>
                                        <select id="newTaskWeek" class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-2.5 sm:p-3 border border-indigo-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none cursor-pointer shadow-sm disabled:opacity-50 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 truncate"></select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div>
                                        <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">Приоритет</label>
                                        <select id="newTaskPriority" class="w-full bg-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl p-2.5 sm:p-3 border border-indigo-200 text-xs sm:text-sm outline-none cursor-pointer shadow-sm focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50">
                                            <option value="high" class="font-bold text-rose-600">🔴 Высокий</option>
                                            <option value="medium" class="font-bold text-amber-600" selected>🟡 Средний</option>
                                            <option value="low" class="font-bold text-slate-500">⚪ Низкий</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <button id="addTaskBtn" class="w-full bg-brand-purple text-white rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors shadow-md disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed">+ Добавить</button>
                            </div>
                            <h3 class="text-xs sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-800 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 sm:mb-4 border-b border-slate-100 pb-2" id="tasksListHeaderLabel">Практики Блока 1</h3>
                            <div id="tasksPreviewList" class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 max-h-[250px] sm:max-h-[300px] overflow-y-auto custom-scrollbar pr-1 sm:pr-2 w-full"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="page-rewards" class="page-view w-full">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-10 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 mb-6 sm:mb-8 w-full min-w-0">
                    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start mb-4 sm:mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4 sm:pb-6 gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full">
                        <div class="w-full min-w-0">
                            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800">Система поощрений</h2>
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1 sm:mt-2">Назначьте себе награды для каждого блока.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-1 sm:p-2 rounded-lg sm:rounded-xl border border-slate-200 flex flex-wrap gap-1 w-full lg:w-auto justify-between">
                            <button class="reward-block-btn flex-1 px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-md sm:rounded-lg text-[9px] sm:text-sm font-bold bg-brand-purple text-white shadow-sm" data-block="1">Блок 1</button>
                            <button class="reward-block-btn flex-1 px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-md sm:rounded-lg text-[9px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors" data-block="2">Блок 2</button>
                            <button class="reward-block-btn flex-1 px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-md sm:rounded-lg text-[9px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors" data-block="3">Блок 3</button>
                            <button class="reward-block-btn flex-1 px-2 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-md sm:rounded-lg text-[9px] sm:text-sm font-bold text-slate-500 hover:bg-slate-200 transition-colors" data-block="4">Блок 4</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-4 sm:p-6 text-white mb-6 sm:mb-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between shadow-lg relative overflow-hidden gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full">
                        <div class="relative z-10 w-full min-w-0">
                            <p class="text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-1" id="rewardFactSubtitle">Факт: Блок 1</p>
                            <div class="flex items-end gap-2 sm:gap-4 flex-wrap">
                                <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-emerald-400" id="rewardFactPct">0%</h3>
