                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="relative z-10 md:text-right w-full md:w-auto">
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm text-slate-300 mb-1.5 sm:mb-2 hidden md:block">Статус:</p>
                            <div id="rewardStatusBadge" class="inline-block w-full md:w-auto text-center px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-full text-[10px] sm:text-sm font-bold bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 border border-slate-700 truncate">Пока не достигнуто</div>
                        </div>
