                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6 w-full" id="rewardsCardsContainer"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="page-reflection" class="page-view w-full">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-10 shadow-sm border border-slate-100 mb-6 sm:mb-8 w-full min-w-0">
                    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-between items-start mb-5 sm:mb-10 border-b border-slate-100 pb-4 sm:pb-8 gap-3 sm:gap-4 w-full">
                        <div class="w-full min-w-0">
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 sm:gap-2 mb-1.5 sm:mb-2">
                                <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] font-bold bg-brand-purple/10 text-brand-purple px-1.5 sm:px-2 py-0.5 sm:py-1 rounded uppercase tracking-wider" id="reflectBlockLabel">Блок 1</span>
                                <span class="text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-medium" id="reflectWeekDates">--</span>
                            </div>
                            <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 truncate" id="reflectWeekTitle">Рефлексия недели</h2>
                            <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1 sm:mt-2">Оцените результаты и проанализируйте срывы.</p>
                        </div>
                        <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm px-3 sm:px-4 py-1.5 sm:py-2 rounded-full text-rose-500 font-bold bg-rose-50 border border-rose-100 shrink-0 w-full lg:w-auto text-center truncate">Выполняем до воскресенья</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-6 sm:gap-10 w-full">
                        <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-8 space-y-5 sm:space-y-8 w-full min-w-0">
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 sm:mb-3">1. Что прошло хорошо (успехи)</label>
                                <textarea id="inputWentWell" class="auto-resize w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-3 sm:p-6 border border-slate-200 min-h-[5rem] sm:min-h-[8rem] text-xs sm:text-sm focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-slate-400 break-words" placeholder="Запишите свои достижения..."></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <label class="block text-[9px] sm:text-xs font-bold text-slate-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 sm:mb-3">2. Срывы и препятствия (проблемы)</label>
                                <textarea id="inputToImprove" class="auto-resize w-full bg-slate-50 rounded-xl sm:rounded-2xl p-3 sm:p-6 border border-slate-200 min-h-[5rem] sm:min-h-[8rem] text-xs sm:text-sm focus:bg-white focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand-purple/50 outline-none transition-all placeholder:text-slate-400 break-words" placeholder="Запишите трудности..."></textarea>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-span-1 lg:col-span-4 space-y-5 sm:space-y-6 w-full min-w-0">
                            <div class="border border-slate-100 rounded-2xl sm:rounded-3xl p-5 sm:p-8 bg-slate-50/50 flex flex-col items-center text-center w-full">
                                <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-sm text-slate-500 mb-1.5 sm:mb-2 font-medium">Общая оценка недели</p>
                                <h3 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-bold text-brand-purple mb-3 sm:mb-4" id="reflectWeekScorePrc">0%</h3>
                                <div class="w-full h-1 sm:h-1.5 bg-slate-200 rounded-full overflow-hidden mb-4 sm:mb-6 max-w-[200px] sm:max-w-none"><div id="reflectWeekScoreBar" class="h-full bg-brand-purple" style="width: 0%"></div></div>
                                
                                <label class="block text-[8px] sm:text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3 sm:mb-4">Рейтинг (Ощущения)</label>
